data.description:
Well maintained, 4-plex located in a very convenient location with two open units for owner occupant opportunity! *Three - 2 bedroom units & One - 1 bedroom unit. *
 1 block to light-rail station and bus stop, plus close to Target, Cub Foods, YWCA and many stores and restaurants! Many updates include: New Roof in 2017, All New Windows in 2015, All Units New Kitchen Cabinets were installed between 2017 and 2019. Most units have new appliances replaced since 2016. 3 Newer water heaters. 3 units had flooring replaced: 2024, 2020, 2017. All furnaces replaced in 2010..and much more! Coin laundry. Tenants pay Electric/Gas. (One unit virtually staged.) *Ask about assumable mortgage.
